{
  "stem": "20405.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And were a kapo-- kapo with a German kapo, a criminal, like I told you, Karlo, name, which at the end we killed them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after we burned the 30,000 Hungarian people, then they start to get some of us and kill them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because was no-- no-- no work anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Russian was coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was no work anymore more to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was no more-- no more transports.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The last ones was the Hungarians, 30,000.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after that, they got some other Hungarians, which I found them in [GERMAN] with the hair again and with some belongings they had.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't have the time to kill them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When there was no more work, that when-- there is where we start-- they were-- they start.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They thought, maybe, was the revolution.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There-- there-- then-- then it started like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you want to hear about it, I can tell you right away for the revolution.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're coming near the revolution now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About the revolt?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll tell you right now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] In the-- in the crematoriums, was working with us a Greek guy, a very short Greek guy, which he was an officer in the Greek army cavalry.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Joseph was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know the second name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe Dario get it, told you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was a military type.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the way it was, the crematoriums, one, two, three, and four, was in each one of them was separated, except the Kanada Kommando, Kanada Kommando.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was streets, which they were coming from Auschwitz form the end of the Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "From the inside of Birkenau, they were coming to the west, to us, walking in those streets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I can make you a design if you want to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rifles and--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
